Tharn, do you really think Montree is the one behind your father’s death, as well as Lieut Tam’s and Kao’s deaths?

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.120
Inspector already knew. Why didn’t he tell us the truth?

00:00:16.120 --> 00:00:18.000
Or maybe, he’s one of Montree’s lackeys?

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.680
Inspector, do you know my father?

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:21.920
Your father was betrayed by someone in his unit.

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:23.120
Your father’s team leader.

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:25.560
We’ll stay here for a week.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.160
We’ll be staying at Tharn’s grandma’s place.

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:28.720
Khem, hurry up and go to Ning’s house.

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:30.840
What did you say? Ning is dead?!

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:33.640
She didn’t leave us any evidence and we couldn’t help her somehow.

00:00:33.640 --> 00:00:35.360
How many times does it have to be like this?!

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:37.520
Gather as many artworks as you can.

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:41.800
This time, it’s going to be a big one. Once you get them, send them to our warehouse in Nongkai.

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.960
[Montree is heading to NongKai, where the NongKai forest produces medicine along the Mekong River.]
It’s one of our workers who went into the woods to collect wild products.

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:46.240
Kai – he was eaten by the Tiger-man.

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.800
Where’s his body right now?

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:54.600
According to the report, the area along the bank of Mekhong river, especially between Thailand-Laos birder,

00:00:54.800 --> 00:01:00.600
is often used as the route to smuggle in drugs from Laos to Thailand...

00:01:00.760 --> 00:01:02.680
...via the natural border path.

00:01:02.960 --> 00:01:07.360
Smugglers also pay local people to load drugs into their boats and secretly made landfall in Thailand.

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:12.280
There are amphetamine, Ice, and also heroin.

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:17.560
We suspect that the place where Montree and his gang use as a shelter and a hub in producing drugs…

00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:21.080
is around the area of national reserved forests in Nongkai.

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:36.320
In this wipe-out mission, we’d be working closely with the forest rangers and the navy force.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:40.400
The forest rangers will assist us during our search in the forest.

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:46.360
The navy force will help provide a backup force during our arrest.

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:50.640
Inspector, aren’t you going to include Phaya and Tharn in this mission?

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:52.000
That’s right, Inspector.

00:01:53.320 --> 00:01:55.840
I think Tharn wants to be included in this mission too.

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:58.440
He’s already in Nongkai, staying at his grandmother’s place.

00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.960
Should I call him?

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:03.040
You know better than anyone how badly Tharn wants to arrest Montree

00:02:03.440 --> 00:02:04.760
Please give him a chance.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.600
Go and get ready.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.800
We’ll leave to Nongkai tomorrow.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:13.680
Yes, sir!

00:02:22.600 --> 00:02:24.520
Yai, you stay.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:31.760
Yes, sir.

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:41.160
I want to know how Tharn knew that Ning was going to get killed.

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:46.800
Well, that’s because...

00:02:52.079 --> 00:02:54.480
he can see a vision or a sign of what’s going to happen.

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:56.520
The sign?

00:02:57.920 --> 00:02:58.640
Yes.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.320
After his accident with his parents,

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:06.400
he started to see all these signs and visions...

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.200
including ones about our cases.

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:11.280
He’s been having a vision ever since.

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:16.480
I’m going to give you one last chance to tell me the truth, Yai.

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:19.160
I ‘am’ telling you the truth, Inspector.

00:03:20.079 --> 00:03:22.680
Tharn can see what’s going to happen beforehand. I really mean it.

