The Sign

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.960
Kham, you have to tell me everything.

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:03.160
I have told you everything that I know.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.640
And they are all the truth.

00:05:10.640 --> 00:05:12.320
Didanyone go into Joe’s room last night?

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:13.960
Umm, I don’t know.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:19.320
It looks like his room was ransacked.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:23.920
Joe is not a tidy person. His room is often in a mess.

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:27.680
He’s untidy and not hygienic.

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:31.400
He doesn’t like to mingle. We barely know him.

00:05:31.960 --> 00:05:33.440
What are you two looking for?

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:36.640
What are you two looking for?

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:41.400
What are you two looking for?

00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:45.440
I’m looking for drugs. Joe’s test result reveals that he has drugs in his body

00:05:45.440 --> 00:05:49.680
Grandma told me you’re the leader here, taking care of all the workers and looking after the sawmill.

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:51.600
Don’t you know that Joe uses drugs?

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:53.080
Not a clue.

00:05:53.640 --> 00:05:55.280
I barely know him.

00:05:56.920 --> 00:06:01.440
What does a Tiger-man look like? Can you show me?

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:04.440
Absolutely not. He’s scary.

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:07.800
He’s half human half ghost. He can transform into a tiger.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:11.800
I’d rather not talk abou it anymore. It’s so scary. I’m off to bed then.

00:06:16.080 --> 00:06:19.800
Hey, why did you try to get on his nerves?

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:22.280
We still need more information from him.

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:24.600
Well, so that I could get some information.

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:27.160
Look here.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.960
Why are these footprints in Joe’s room?

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:39.120
He doesn’t like to mingle. We barely know him.

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:42.960
He’s untidy and not hygienic.

00:06:43.080 --> 00:06:44.560
What are you two looking for?

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:46.360
You heard what he said.

00:06:46.840 --> 00:06:48.480
Joe hardly talks to anyone.

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.960
Then why there are Kham’s footprints in Joe’s room.

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:57.640
I think he’s hiding something from us.

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.600
Tharn, go and look upstairs.

00:07:57.200 --> 00:07:58.640
- Found anything?
- No.

00:08:17.200 --> 00:08:19.080
(Door unlocking)

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:36.360
Hey, come and have a look here.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:41.520
(Exciting sound)

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:58.160
This definitely has something to do with drugs like what you think.

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:02.400
Then we must hurry up and find the body of that worker.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:04.680
We can use it as an evidence to arrest Kham.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.360
Why are you calling Chalothorn?

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:32.560
I’m going to ask him about giving our workers a drug test.

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:35.200
Can’t you call some other doctors instead?

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:37.880
But I only trust Doc.

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:38.920
But I don’t trust him.

00:09:45.560 --> 00:09:49.000
Phaya, give me back my phone.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:53.000
Let me take care of the drug test matter.

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:56.520
No, you stay out of it. This is my family’s matter.

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.720
I can take care of it.

00:09:59.040 --> 00:10:00.320
Aren’t I one of your family too?

00:10:00.680 --> 00:10:01.880
Am I not the one you love?

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:07.400
Phaya, about Doc and I, you know I only think of him as my brother.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:10.160
So, please stop being jealous. Can’t you guys just be friends?

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:14.560
As long as Chalothorn is still in your life,

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:16.360
I’ll never stop getting in the way

00:10:17.560 --> 00:10:21.600
It’s all right if you don’t trust him. But can’t you just trust me?

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:23.800
Why are you like this?

00:10:23.800 --> 00:10:26.200
What has he done to you? Why do you hate him so much?

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:27.640
Because he’s the Naga!

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.960
the one who kept us apart in our past lives.

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:42.360
He’s the one who tried to kill me and take you away from me.

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:47.080
That drowning that almost killed me, it was because of him.

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:48.960
He was trying to kill me.

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:53.640
I never thought you’d be like this. Just because you don’t want me to get close to him,

00:10:53.800 --> 00:10:55.600
you even came up with this nonsense.

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:58.520
Hey, I didn’t make it up. I’m telling you the truth.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:02.120
If you don’t believe me, let’s go ask the Abbot. He knows everything

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:06.560
That’s enough. I’m going to let it slide and ignore what you just said.

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:08.480
But don’t ever mention it to me again.

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:10.040
I have an important job to do.

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:14.360
Kai’s body must be in this forest. I have to find it.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:21.200
(Thunder sound)

00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:24.240
(Thunder and lightening)

00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:40.680
(Thunder and lightening)

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:43.920
(Sighs)

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:47.000
(Thunder and lightening)

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:53.000
Your time is coming, isn’t it?

00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:20.840
Don’t worry, I’ll take care of him for you.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:23.200
Don’t you worry.

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:39.840
(Door knocking)

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:44.960
Tharn, come out and eat something, dear.

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:48.360
Don’t lock yourself in there.

00:12:50.280 --> 00:12:51.360
(Door knocking)

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:52.560
Tharn.

00:12:53.680 --> 00:12:54.640
(Door knocking)

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:56.120
Tharn

00:12:59.800 --> 00:13:02.200
(Door opening.)

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:08.120
Who are you? Why are you in my grandson’s room?

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:12.240
When the time comes, you and I will finally be together.

00:13:23.200 --> 00:13:24.240
Grandma.

00:13:28.920 --> 00:13:31.360
I miss you so much.

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:35.520
Aww, don’t sweet talk me.

00:13:35.560 --> 00:13:38.600
Where’s that friend of yours that you want to introduce to me?

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:42.000
He’s outside. Let me introduce him to you.

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:47.680
Doc.

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:56.600
Here he is, Grandma. The one I want to introduce to you.

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:14.320
Phaya, please protect Tharn

00:14:47.280 --> 00:14:48.920
Grandmas,

00:14:49.080 --> 00:14:50.920
please eat something.

00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:53.520
Both of you haven’t eaten anything since last night.

00:14:53.920 --> 00:14:55.960
I’m afraid you two might faint.

00:14:58.200 --> 00:15:00.840
I hardly slept last night too.

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:03.800
I heard a loud and scary noise from the forest

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:08.280
Or maybe, it really came from the Tiger-man.

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:16.760
I'm not hungry.

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:20.760
Your brother has disappeared into the woods with Tharn since last night.

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.640
And he’s not answering my call.

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:28.920
Please let both of them come back safely.

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:35.120
The cops already told them they would take care of it but they never listened.

00:15:36.760 --> 00:15:40.760
I’m afraid we won’t be having a vacation this time.

00:15:52.840 --> 00:15:54.800
Oh! Grandmas!

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:56.520
They are back.

00:15:56.520 --> 00:15:57.240
Huh?

00:15:58.760 --> 00:16:00.120
Phaya! Tharn!

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:03.600
Are you all right? We have been worried sick about you.

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:06.280
You just disappeared and didn’t answer my call too.

00:16:06.280 --> 00:16:08.200
We went looking for some evidence about Joe’s case.

00:16:08.600 --> 00:16:09.880
But we found nothing.

00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:11.960
Sorry for keeping you waiting and worrying about us.

00:16:12.640 --> 00:16:14.000
Joe still refuses to say anything.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:18.200
He keeps insisting that Kai was killed by the Tiger-man.

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:23.400
But according to the drug test, we found drugs in his body.

00:16:24.440 --> 00:16:27.920
Grandma, can I go seach Joe’s shelter?

00:16:29.880 --> 00:16:31.800
Since it’s happening with our workers,

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:33.640
I’m worried about you.

00:16:37.240 --> 00:16:41.800
Let’s go and talk inside, shall we?

00:16:42.520 --> 00:16:43.280
Tharn.

00:16:44.680 --> 00:16:46.120
Can I have a word with you?

00:17:09.720 --> 00:17:11.800
You don’t look good, are you okay?

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:18.599
I have a bad feeling.

00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:22.200
Like that time when I lost your parents.

00:17:23.240 --> 00:17:25.839
Looks like that bad feeling is coming back.

00:17:26.520 --> 00:17:28.640
What the Abbot used to tell me...

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:32.000
when you were very young,

00:17:37.080 --> 00:17:39.720
I don’t want it to happen to you again.

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:42.040
I can only pray...

00:17:43.240 --> 00:17:44.920
what the Abbot said

00:17:46.360 --> 00:17:48.000
about that someone...

00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:54.360
who’d be able to protect you

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:58.280
would be Phaya.

00:18:00.120 --> 00:18:01.960
I know you’re worried about me.

00:18:04.160 --> 00:18:06.520
But everything that’s happening here,

00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:10.040
might lead me to find the person who killed my parents.

00:18:13.120 --> 00:18:14.680
I’m a police officer after all.

00:18:15.280 --> 00:18:16.920
I have my father’s blood in me.

00:18:19.720 --> 00:18:22.280
I can feel that eveything is going to end soon.

00:18:23.400 --> 00:18:24.920
The person who killed dad,

00:18:25.920 --> 00:18:28.920
the one who created all these terrible things,

00:18:30.040 --> 00:18:33.400
and also drugs network with Montree being the man behind it all,

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:36.520
all of these must be connected in some way.

00:18:37.400 --> 00:18:40.080
I’m going to find a solid evidence to take them down.

00:18:47.680 --> 00:18:49.200
I promise I’ll be careful.

00:18:51.040 --> 00:18:53.280
I’ll infrom my unit as soon as I can,

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:56.160
and will ask them to send me a backup team.

00:18:57.400 --> 00:18:58.840
I promise....

00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:04.560
not to do anything on impluse and make you worried.

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:11.680
I know I can’t stop you.

00:19:13.640 --> 00:19:15.840
So, please always stay focus.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:19.080
If what the Abbot said is true,

00:19:20.560 --> 00:19:26.000
that person is coming to take you back.

00:19:36.600 --> 00:19:40.960
Yes,sir. I’ll send you some artworks as a gift then.

00:19:41.520 --> 00:19:43.120
(Laughing)

00:19:43.680 --> 00:19:45.480
Yes. Thank you, sir.

00:19:49.240 --> 00:19:50.040
Hey.

00:19:51.080 --> 00:19:53.640
Send someone to deliver the gift to our dear sir tomorrow.

00:19:53.800 --> 00:19:55.600
Don’t forget to take a picture too.

00:19:55.800 --> 00:19:58.800
Just in case they might betray us. I’m not going to let them get away so easily.

00:19:59.160 --> 00:20:00.120
Yes, sir.

00:20:00.640 --> 00:20:03.040
Have you sent someone to that side to load in the drugs?

00:20:03.640 --> 00:20:05.240
- Working on it, sir.
- Okay.

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:10.080
Hey, you. The one holding the gun.

00:20:11.120 --> 00:20:14.000
You go with Khom so that you can learn from him.

00:20:15.080 --> 00:20:15.800
Yes, sir.

00:20:16.360 --> 00:20:17.080
Good.

00:20:17.960 --> 00:20:20.480
After this shipping lot, I might have to take a break for a while.

00:20:20.480 --> 00:20:22.920
Inspector Akk is keeping an eye on me.

00:20:23.880 --> 00:20:25.320
I have to get rid of him.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:13.560
I want someone who knows the route that Joe and Kai took

00:21:13.840 --> 00:21:15.360
when they went into the woods that day.

00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:17.440
I’ll pay you 10,000 baht.

00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:19.640
Does anyone want to volunteer?

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:31.040
Or just tell me how much you want.

00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:34.720
I don’t think anyone would want to take you into the woods.

00:21:35.320 --> 00:21:38.040
They are all afraid of the Tiger-man.

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:42.520
Don’t worry, a Tiger-man is not real.

00:21:42.720 --> 00:21:45.000
Joe was having a hallucination because he used drugs.

00:21:45.360 --> 00:21:48.440
The test result has confirmed that Joe had drugs in his body.

00:21:49.280 --> 00:21:52.400
Fine then, if that’s what you want to believe.

00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:56.360
But we believe he was killed and eaten by the Tiger-man.

00:21:56.360 --> 00:21:57.240
Right?

00:21:57.440 --> 00:21:58.640
Yeah, yeah.

00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:00.240
Let me warn you.

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:04.680
If you go into that woods and get attacked by the Tiger-man, we’re not going to help you.

00:22:05.640 --> 00:22:06.760
Does anyone still want to go with them?

00:22:07.360 --> 00:22:08.160
No.

00:22:09.240 --> 00:22:11.280
Whatever. We’re off to work now.

00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:12.880
Hurry up.

00:22:34.720 --> 00:22:37.800
